                "question": "What is the finFET device dimensions after ALE?",
                "answer_type": "Paragraph",
                "answer": "After 162 cycles of thermal ALE with HF/DMAC 300 \u00b0C with PDMAC = 40 mTorr, \n1. Fin width, Wf ranged from 2.5 to 18 nm\n2. Gate length, Lg was 60 nm."
